      <title>由于较高的收益率吸引买家，英国债券需求打破纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/uk-five-year-bond-sale-receives-record-demand-at-auction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府债券拍卖获得创纪录的超额认购，数月来的最高收益率再次吸引了买家，缓解了人们对发行过剩将削弱人们对证券兴趣的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/uk-five-year-bond-sale-receives-record-demand-at-auction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:25:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
